Mu '''2019 Africa Movie Academy Awards''' umuhango wabaye ku cyumweru 27 Ukwakira 2019 ijoro ritazibagirana kuri Event Centre muri Lagos, [[Nijeriya|Nigeria]] . Ibirori byamenyekanye kandi bihesha icyubahiro indashyikirwa mu bayobozi, abakinnyi, n'abanditsi mu bijyanye na firime. Ijoro ryo gutanga ibihembo ryakiriwe na Kemi Lala Akindoju, Lorenzo Menakaya na Funnybone. Nyuma yo kwakira inyandiko zigera kuri 700 zatanzwe hagati yitariki ya 21 Ukwakira 2018 na 26 Mutarama 2019, abateguye ibirori batangaje abatoranijwe ku ya 19 Nzeri 2019.    ''Umuhungu wo Gutanga'' no ''kudoda imbeho kuruhu rwanjye'' yayoboye hamwe nomination 13 buriwese mugihe ''[[The Burial of Kojo|Gushyingura Kojo]]'' na ''Redemption'' byakurikiranye na 10 buri umwe.  ''Impuhwe z'ishyamba'' zatsindiye mu byiciro bya Filime Nziza, Ibyagezweho mu Gushushanya Imyambarire, Ibyagezweho muri Makiya n'umukinnyi mwiza mu mwanya wa mbere . Politiki ishimishije ''King of Boys'' yatwaye ibihembo bitatu muri iryo joro rimwe, harimo ibihembo byumukinnyi witwaye neza mu nshingano zunganira, umukinnyi wa filime mwiza, ndetse na Filime nziza yo muri Nigeriya . 
